{"tid":1119740,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"翁靜晶與何東爵士曾孫何彪6月舉行婚禮　翁靜晶正式成為何東家族成員","createTime":"2019-04-22T06:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T07:19:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25f0e3b980f576ee90318d3d1c08ff46877dd759","tid":1119740,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:59:56.000Z","msg":"現年54歲的翁靜晶，與何東爵士的曾孫何彪（Sean，原名何猷彪）拍拖數年、屢傳婚訊，近日有消息<br />\n流出指二人將於6月8日舉行婚禮正式拉埋天窗，翁靜晶將成為「何東媳婦」！<br />\n翁靜晶與比她年輕1歲的何彪於2010年被影到親密出遊，直到2015年才公開拍拖。但於2011年底，社交網站上見到二人帳號顯示關係為「戀愛中」，翌年1月更改為「已婚」。<br />\n其實早有傳媒於2015年在翁靜晶與何彪公開關係後，詢問社交網帳號寫「已婚」一事，她回應指估計是何彪家人為他們開設的帳號。估計當時前夫劉家良因癌症病逝不久，她顧及兩位女兒劉萬儀與劉幸儀的感受，翁靜晶犧牲個人幸福，與男友沒打算結婚。<br />\n在過去數年來，翁靜晶與何彪感情穩定，兼且二人理念一致，何彪與翁靜晶一同打擊「假和尚」。<br />\n何彪家族亦是愛護動物人士，早前翁靜晶於歐洲遇到兩隻狗Blue和Jack，全靠何彪全力幫助，終於成功將兩狗帶到香港繼續撫養。<br />\n他們十分思愛，非常甜蜜，曾被傳媒影到牽手走在街頭，對望時仍情不自禁地擁吻，濃情蜜意滿瀉。<br />\n據知翁靜晶家族與何家是世交，故男友家人一直對她非常鍾愛，希望他們盡快拉埋天窗。早前已傳出翁靜晶再婚傳聞，當時提及男友何彪時，她在個人facbook甜蜜地謂：「感恩有此知音人。」但對婚訊傳聞卻未有正面回應。<br />\n直到近日有知情人士透露，翁靜晶與何彪將於6月8日舉行禮結婚，結束多年愛情長跑，正式給予對方名份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2330000/2331873/MaryJeanReimer_thumb_20190422_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2330000%2F2331873%2FMaryJeanReimer_thumb_20190422_ch_1024.jpg&h=f3afd34f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2330000/2331873/_2019041112353474620_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2330000%2F2331873%2F_2019041112353474620_1024.jpg&h=ab273308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2330000/2331873/1_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2330000%2F2331873%2F1_1024.JPG&h=8664f9fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2331873/%E7%BF%81%E9%9D%9C%E6%99%B6%E8%88%87%E4%BD%95%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%B5%E5%A3%AB%E6%9B%BE%E5%AD%AB%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%AA6%E6%9C%88%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E5%A9%9A%E7%A6%AE%E3%80%80%E7%BF%81%E9%9D%9C%E6%99%B6%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E6%9D%B1%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2331873%2F%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%259D%259C%25E6%2599%25B6%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%259D%25B1%25E7%2588%25B5%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BD%25AA6%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25A9%259A%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%259D%259C%25E6%2599%25B6%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6gqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=80badf51\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2331873/%E7%BF%81%E9%9D%9C%E6%99%B6%E8%88%87%E4%BD%95%E6%9D%B1%E7%88%B5%E5%A3%AB%E6%9B%BE%E5%AD%AB%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%AA6%E6%9C%88%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E5%A9%9A%E7%A6%AE%E3%80%80%E7%BF%81%E9%9D%9C%E6%99%B6%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E6%9D%B1%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"fd91db28a75fd190116f4a504a4b359204912093","tid":1119740,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"又翻頭嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa2875d604ac000e1a472e707d84d26b281c434","tid":1119740,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}